{"title":"走近虎门","authors":["杨子江钟鸣"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":12,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近虎门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨子江钟鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮声在上个世纪响过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐远了而炮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在还醒着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着那条宽敞的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿就到了那个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令民族心颤的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种名叫鸦片的东西"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面目狰狞地楔在近代史的伤口里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殷殷的血仍在流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴滴都含着烟的味道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个偌大的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能倒伏在鸦片的脚下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林则徐用了一个时代的勇气　重重地拍了拍桌子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那威严如枪口一般的眼神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今还那么力量无穷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近虎门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都可以"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带你到心跳最烈的位置"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}